      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GOODNIGHT JASPER (1) turned in a good run last time, finishing in the placings (29.92) at this track in a Grade 6. Lines up from box 1 for the first time. Well-placed to take this out. FLYING CAROLINE (4) had a tricky draw last time and although midfield in fourth wasn't far away finishing 3.5 lengths from the winner (26.38). Likely to play a prominent role. IRISHTOWN (7) shows ability but remains a maiden after 12 starts. Was below best last time when missed the frame finishing fifth (26.47) at Hobart. Key runner on best form. SCARRED (6) warrants respect although new to this distance.",
